  "time_ut": 1660888170,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dbb\u0dda \u0db4\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0db8\u0db1\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0dc5 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dba \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dcf\u0da2\u0db4\u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dc2 \u0d86\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba\u0dda \u0d86\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dca\u0db7\u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The attack on the Antare march was the beginning of the end of the Ranil Rajapaksa government",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The National Bhikshu Peramuna says in a statement that the water and tear gas attacks and the baton attack on the protest march held by the Inter-University Student Union is the final attack of the Ranil Rajapaksa government. The front said in a statement that it strongly protested and condemned the attack.",
        "\"We as National Bhikshu Peramuna would like to point out that if the Ranil Pohottu government, which is unable to solve the problems of the people that arise day by day, is thinking of suppressing the demands of the people, it is a very foolish idea. Instead of looking for answers to the acute crises of the people, the President Wickremesinghe is trying to find answers to the acute crises of the people. The people are well aware that the camp is working to protect its existence and to protect criminals and corrupt people.",
        "It is the wish of the people to free the country from Ranilla and Rajapaksa and maintain it under populist rule. When 3 out of 10 families of the people of the country are starving, when people are dying due to lack of necessary medicines, the people have no choice but to take to the streets against the idiotic practices of the government which is issuing cabinet papers to give compensation to white cloth thieves, killers of Tamil children and central bank robbers.",
        "Pereida fishermen. Yesterday's students, tomorrow's farmers, by the next day all the masses will be on the streets. Must get off.",
        "Millions of Sri Lankan people who have lost their lives and livelihoods due to Ranilla's and Japakshala's brutal rule must demand their lives and fill all the avenues tomorrow to achieve their victories.",
        "The rulers who destroyed the country for 74 years should no longer be allowed to kill the people of Suwase. Therefore, except for the idiotic rulers of the corrupt Ranil Rajapaksa government and a handful of people who are helping it, everyone should take to the streets, struggle, kick out all kinds of corrupt people for 74 years, and build a populist government. For that, we request all Sri Lankans to stand up and come together without being afraid of the repressions of the anti-people government that has no popular opinion.",
        "We urge the government to immediately stop the repression of arresting people, including the convener, and to immediately release all those who were arrested."
      ],
